Burstroem's Browser*
Forged in the magical land of Scandinavia by Burstroem the BattleMage.  
This object empowers the owner with limited Lexmnemancy.  It allows the
owning wizard to browse through other wizard's spell-lists to see what
spells they have.

During the spell-selection phase, just press CTRL-# to browse through
another player's spell-list.  E.  G.  press ctrl-2 to peek at player 2's
spell-list.
